    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deo M<supplied reason="lost">agno</supplied> <lb n="2"/>Aeter<supplied reason="lost">no synago</supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/>gam pr<supplied reason="lost">oseucham</supplied> <lb n="4"/>a <supplied reason="lost">solo</supplied> <lb n="5"/>Claudia P<supplied reason="lost">ia<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="6"/>OVE pecun<supplied reason="lost">ia sua</supplied> <lb n="7"/>fecit ex v<supplied reason="lost">oto</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 5/6: möglicherweise P[ia pro se suis]/que. Z. 2-5: Ergänzungsvorschlag weitgehend nach Tóth; Z. 5/6: Tóth: P[ia? filio]/que(?). Z. 2-6: Ergänzungsvorschlag Gáspár: domum lon]/gam pr[o se et suis] / A[urelia] / Claudia P[ia filio]/que.</p>
            </div>
